The evidence with the title 'Socialized medicine: the horror movie | Economic Policy Institute ' says Oct 1, 2013  ... My sister - in - law Liz — an American — lives in London , where they really do have socialized medicine in the form of the government -runNationalHealthService(NHS). ... Only when the public can see clearly that there are workable alternatives will we reform our perverse “ free market ” health care system . 
